  <summary>2/9/1987--Introduced.
FmHA Leadership Act of 1987 - Amends the Consolidated Farm and Rural Development Act to provide for loan principal reductions for marginal farm borrowers. Defines "marginal borrower" as a borrower who would not otherwise be able to meet his debt obligations unless the outstanding loan principal were reduced to the value of the securing property.</summary>
